name: Thule Hull-a-Port Kayak Rack
description: These unique J-shaped holders fit most sea and whitewater kayaks and are padded to gently cradle your boat. The angled design allows more room for other boats or carrier boxes on your rack.Fits Thule® SquareBar and WingBar and most factory-installed roof racks.Includes 2 straps with buckle protectors.Wide-mouth J-shaped profile offers easier loading and unloading.Steel design with injected molded nylon is very durable.Rust-resistant coating and hardware for longer product life.
